: Rowman &amp; Littlefield, 2008); N. Mark Lam and John L. Graham, <i>China Now: Doing Business in the World’s Most Dynamic Market</i> (New York: McGraw-Hill, 2007); and Philip R. Cateora, Mary C. Gilly, and John L. Graham, <i>International Marketing</i> (14th edition, Burr Ridge, IL: McGraw-Hill, 2009).</li>
